<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-63-0843 </DOCNO><TEXT>A new Standard, ISO 3171 (Italy), for on-line automatic sampling, establishesinternational rules for oil vendors, buyers and carriers. It describesdevices and operating procedures for obtaining acceptable samples. Calculationmethods can be applied to predict and verify the state of homogeneityof water in oil, one of the mandatory conditions for a sampling operation.Practical recommendations for users are given, based on both theory andexperience.</TEXT></DOC>